ProtoDefines:
. "Let $B$ be a positive integer. If $n$ is a positive integer
   with prime factorization $n=\prod p_i^{e_i}$, then $n$ is 
   {\em $B$-power smooth} if $p_i^{e_i}\leq B$ for all $i$."
